WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.470
Shunday qilib, bu kamalak ranglari ro‘yxati bilan qilishimiz mumkin bo‘lgan yana bir narsa.

00:00:04.470 --> 00:00:09.910
Ushbu turtle oltita turli xil rangdagi yulduzlarni chizishi va joriy dars buni qanday amalga oshirish haqida.

00:00:09.910 --> 00:00:15.420
Yuqoridan, biz turtle ni aniqlab, turtle kengligini beshga o‘rnatdik,

00:00:15.420 --> 00:00:17.280
bunda ular chiroyli va jonli bo‘lishadi.

00:00:17.280 --> 00:00:23.060
Men tezlikni nolga sozlayapman, u juda tez, shuning uchun u juda tez chizadi.

00:00:23.720 --> 00:00:27.180
Keyin biz kamalak ranglarini berish uchun sikl olamiz.

00:00:27.180 --> 00:00:30.210
Shunday qilib, ushbu rang o‘zgaruvchisi 

00:00:30.210 --> 00:00:34.075
har safar ushbu sikldan o‘tganimizda ro‘yxatdan keyingi qiymatni oladi,

00:00:34.075 --> 00:00:36.895
qizil, keyin zarg‘algoq, keyin sariq va hokazo.

00:00:36.895 --> 00:00:41.840
Birinchi bosqichda biz turtle ning rangini belgilaymiz, keyin

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:45.370
bizda 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 tomonlar uchun ichki sikl bor.

00:00:45.370 --> 00:00:49.335
bu bitta yulduz chizadi.

00:00:49.335 --> 00:00:51.530
Bitta yulduzni chizgandan keyin,

00:00:51.530 --> 00:00:55.870
siklning qolgan kodi keyingi yulduz joyiga o‘tkazadi.

00:00:55.870 --> 00:00:59.925
60 ga o‘ngga burilib, qalamni yuqoriga ko‘taradi,

00:00:59.925 --> 00:01:05.200
bitta yulduzdan ikkinchi yulduzga o‘tish uchun 50 pikselga siljiydi,

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:06.885
va qalamni pastga qo‘yadi.

00:01:06.885 --> 00:01:09.020
Keyin, biz siklning yuqori qismiga o‘tamiz,

00:01:09.020 --> 00:01:12.410
yangi rang olib yangi yulduz chizamiz.

